<p><br></p>

<blockquote>
  <p><code>Anonymous</code> function expressions <a href="https://jsperf.com/named-vs-anonymous-expressions" rel="noreferrer">appear to have better performance</a>
  against <code>Named</code> function expression.</p>
</blockquote>

